{{define "done"}}
<div class="text-center py-6">
  <div class="mx-auto w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 dark:bg-emerald-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-7 w-7 text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
    </svg>
  </div>
  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-1 text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Install complete</h2>
  <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mb-6">
    The wizard is locked. The panel pushed a self-bootstrap route to your
    first Caddy node, so the public address you entered now reverse-proxies
    back to this app - sign in there, not on this temporary URL.
  </p>

  {{if .Form.AppURL}}
  <div class="mb-6 text-left bg-slate-50 dark:bg-zinc-800/60 border border-slate-200 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:border-zinc-700 rounded-lg p-4 text-xs text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 space-y-2">
    <div><strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Public panel URL:</strong> <a href="{{.Form.AppURL}}" class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 underline break-all">{{.Form.AppURL}}</a></div>
    <div><strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Before you sign in there:</strong> point a DNS A record for that hostname at your Caddy node's public IP, then wait one Let's Encrypt issuance cycle (~30s on first hit).</div>
    <div class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">If you forgot the IP or want to add more hosts, sign in via the local URL below first, then jump to /admin/hosts/new.</div>
  </div>
  {{end}}

  <div class="flex justify-center gap-3">
    {{if .Form.AppURL}}
    <a href="{{.Form.AppURL}}/auth/login" class="inline-block px-5 py-2 rounded-md bg-indigo-600 text-white text-sm font-medium hover:bg-indigo-700">
      Sign in at panel URL →
    </a>
    {{end}}
    <a href="/auth/login" class="inline-block px-5 py-2 rounded-md border border-slate-300 dark:border-zinc-700 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800">
      Sign in locally
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
{{end}}
